  "comment_text": {
    "sn43.13:1.1": "Here begins a series of synonyms for Nibbāna the unconditioned. I provide a comment for the less common term. | “Uninclined” (<i lang='pi' translate='no'>anata</i>) occurs at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/ud8.2/en/sujato#3.1'>Ud 8.2:3.1</a>. See <a href='https://suttacentral.net/sn12.40/en/sujato#1.4'>SN 12.40:1.4</a> and <a href='https://suttacentral.net/sn35.87/en/sujato#11.5'>SN 35.87:11.5</a> and notes. "
  },
